      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Paytm 创始人 Sharma 期望银行恢复业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/paytm-founder-sharma-expects-bank-to-get-back-into-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Paytm 的创始人希望，在将 Paytm 与其更大的金融科技帝国划清界限后，他的银行能从印度监管机构获得新的生机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/paytm-founder-sharma-expects-bank-to-get-back-into-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 13:58:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
